WEBVTT

00:03.440 --> 00:04.560
As for this marriage

00:04.560 --> 00:06.120
It mainly depends on fate

00:06.160 --> 00:07.320
Have that girl called

00:07.560 --> 00:08.720
Wan'er

00:08.760 --> 00:09.880
Have her birth characters

00:09.880 --> 00:11.440
Sent to the Ministry of Rites for calculation

00:11.600 --> 00:12.880
To see if they match

00:13.320 --> 00:15.000
Thank you, Your Majesty, thank you, Father

00:15.320 --> 00:16.040
Enough

00:16.440 --> 00:17.320
All dismissed

00:26.440 --> 00:27.440
This marriage

00:27.440 --> 00:29.640
Was requested before all the court officials

00:30.000 --> 00:31.640
Once it's settled

00:31.640 --> 00:32.320
It means

00:32.320 --> 00:33.640
Your Majesty has tacitly approved

00:33.640 --> 00:35.880
Prince of Ning and the Chen family further bound together

00:36.040 --> 00:37.160
Once they gain momentum

00:38.000 --> 00:39.560
Those who are watching

00:39.560 --> 00:41.720
Will gradually align with Prince of Ning

00:41.880 --> 00:43.320
Your subject has also learned

00:43.600 --> 00:45.160
General Zu Kun from the north

00:45.160 --> 00:46.880
Is about to return to court to report

00:47.360 --> 00:48.000
It's said

00:48.000 --> 00:49.160
The vanguard troops

00:49.160 --> 00:50.320
Have already camped outside the city

00:50.560 --> 00:51.200
The Zu family

00:51.200 --> 00:52.760
Has always been neutral

00:53.320 --> 00:53.880
If

00:53.880 --> 00:54.880
At this time

00:54.880 --> 00:56.560
They are swayed

00:56.880 --> 00:57.480
Then

00:57.560 --> 00:59.160
It would be terrible

00:59.440 --> 01:00.640
Though the marriage is small

01:00.720 --> 01:01.880
Its implications are great

01:02.440 --> 01:03.920
Your Majesty ordered the Ministry of Rites to check compatibility

01:03.920 --> 01:05.880
Likely wants to reconsider

01:06.360 --> 01:06.880
Your Highness

01:07.160 --> 01:08.320
We must find a way

01:08.320 --> 01:09.760
To ruin this marriage

01:10.760 --> 01:11.440
I understand

01:11.760 --> 01:12.280
This old minister

01:12.280 --> 01:13.760
Will visit various parties again

01:13.840 --> 01:15.760
And think of other solutions

01:22.880 --> 01:23.600
Mother

01:23.720 --> 01:25.760
Your son has made many arrangements

01:26.600 --> 01:27.640
Your son Sikong Yao

01:27.920 --> 01:29.000
Pays respects to Mother

01:29.760 --> 01:31.000
Yao'er is here

01:31.320 --> 01:31.840
Second brother

01:31.840 --> 01:32.320
Quick

01:32.600 --> 01:34.120
Quick, let Yao'er come in

01:39.440 --> 01:40.360
Elder brother is here too

01:40.760 --> 01:41.440
Second brother

01:43.480 --> 01:44.200
You

01:44.600 --> 01:46.200
Haven't visited Mother in so long

01:47.320 --> 01:48.560
Hurry and apologize to Mother

01:48.760 --> 01:49.640
By kowtowing

01:49.920 --> 01:50.560
Mother

01:51.040 --> 01:52.040
Your son is not in the palace

01:52.320 --> 01:53.480
And hasn't visited often

01:53.880 --> 01:55.040
Please forgive me, Mother

01:55.320 --> 01:56.560
Alright, alright

01:57.040 --> 01:58.200
That you came to see me

01:58.440 --> 01:59.840
Makes me very happy

02:01.440 --> 02:03.560
Today is truly a joyous day

02:04.360 --> 02:05.360
My Zheng'er

02:05.760 --> 02:06.800
And Yao'er

02:07.480 --> 02:08.920
Have both come to visit me

02:10.040 --> 02:10.880
Xiaoqing

02:12.040 --> 02:13.240
Go get the pastry boxes

02:13.240 --> 02:15.040
I made the other day

02:19.600 --> 02:20.360
What's wrong?

02:21.240 --> 02:22.240
Your Majesty

02:22.560 --> 02:24.760
You previously gave the pastries to us servants

02:24.920 --> 02:26.360
Now only one remains

02:27.880 --> 02:29.600
Oh, my memory

02:30.120 --> 02:31.360
Making them now

02:31.560 --> 02:32.800
Is too late
